Eddie Quillan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Quillan 0 Edward Quillan (March 31, 1907 – July 19, 1990) was an American film actor and singer whose career began as a child on the vaudeville stages and silent film and continued through the age of television in the 1980s.
